column5: That's a good pic, it raises a lot of questions.  anything could be happening.
Yah he told Jed if he took a picture of his face he'd use that 9mm that's on his belt !
How do U think my hat got all tattered and torn?
Nothing worse than getting that index figer pointed in your face, my dad use to do it all the time and I knew it was trouble after that.  Or when this guy did it. lol.
Must be a friendly encounter or he'd have his gun hand free and the glove off the right hand.
hey THATS ME  carp SLAP, nope just covering his face, he didnt want his face photographed..  thanks paul  dave
What is going on Clampet?  Can't tell anything from this pic  I know I'm paying big bucks for a fishing license and want the CO's out checking people.  What is going on?

That pic is of me (orange suit)  The CO is named Mitch.   he was checking licenses and we asked him to take his photo for out post.  He didnt want his face photographed so Iwas covering it up when Paul took the pic  DAVE
Little (?) boy caught by the school teacher, fesses up.
You need to seek some profesional help and try to find deep within yerself a smidgeon of a sense of humour, otherwise you will give yerself a CORONARY.
Yeah I've met a few I'd like to slap upside the head too.
